
	<h2>KDE4</h2>

	<p>### FIXME: KDE3 & KDE4 PLANS FOR LENNY ###</p>

	<p>KDE 4 packages are currently in the experimental branch and are not intended to be installed on a production system.  We are not currently accepting bug reports against the KDE4 packages, since they have many known problems.</p>

	<p>If you want to try KDE4, it is recommended that you use <a href="kde4livecd.html">the KDE4 live CD</a>.</p>

	<p>If you are feeling adventurous, you can install the <a href="experimental.html">KDE4 packages from experimental</a>.</p>

	<br />

	<p>If you want to help us get KDE4 ready, you're welcome to <a href="join.html">join the team</a>!</p>
